The paper discusses the security of blockchain systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the study of multiple agents and their strategies, which can be classified under distributed computing (cs.DC) and game theory (cs.GT). The use of hash rate and mining reward also suggests a connection to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
